text: Mustafino () is a rural locality (a village) in Allaguvatsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 184 in 2010. There are three streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Sterlibashevo, 1 km from Nizhny Allaguvat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Mustafino, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
